=Generate a professional and friendly payment reminder email for the following invoice:

Client Name: {{ $json.client_name }}
Invoice Number: {{ $json.invoice_number }}
Amount: {{ $json.currency }} {{ $json.invoice_amount }}
Issue Date: {{ $json.issue_date }}
Due Date: {{ $json.due_date }}
Days Overdue: {{ $json.daysOverdue }}
Reminder Type: {{ $json.reminderType }}
Urgency: {{ $json.urgencyLevel }}

The email should:
- Be courteous and professional
- Clearly state the outstanding amount and invoice details
- Mention the due date and overdue status if applicable
- Include a polite call-to-action for payment
- Provide payment instructions or link
- Be appropriately urgent based on the reminder type
- End with a professional signature

Format the response as a complete email with subject line.

